reply.author: Behance Inc.
reply.content: After installing the Behance Watch Faces it might some time to sync to your watch. Once synced, the watch faces will show up on the watch and in the Android Wear App. You can uninstall the app from your handheld device in settings / apps. If you’re still having issues please email us at androidnetwork@behancenetwork.zendesk.com. Thanks!
